!Announcement!

From the beginning, our show has existed for one purpose: to bring people joy. In the last four years we’ve experienced a lot. Highs and lows (mostly highs). Victories and defeats (mostly victories). But In the midst of it all we’ve never lost sight of the fact that we only exist because of you.

 In 2023 we want to continue to create avenues for you to escape the pressures of everyday life, even if just for a little while.  We will be announcing live shows sporadically, the first batch (Southeast US) in Mid January, as well as other new ventures and projects that we are really excited about. 

Thank you for allowing us to do what we do. From all of us at the Sunny Coast Clubhouse, FMOFM en Espanõl & the entire Florida Men on Florida Man team, we love you. See you soon.

Oh, Florida! 🐊🍊

I made this sunshine state-inspired palette to celebrate the release of my interview with @fmofmpodcast today!

I sat down and somehow got much more vulnerable about my creative journey than anticipated. I told alllll the details of steps forward and steps back and where I am now. And I really hope that a piece of my story can help you process parts of your story too.

It was a delight to have this Florida-filled conversation. The guys are hilarious and kind and I think you’ll love it! Especially if you need a burst of hope today. 

You can listen through the link in my bio or right here: https://open.spotify.com/episode/1fJEqYdXumzClGIi5zMv05?si=IQXIRP9lRSe4sFoQBujv4Q
